.RS
.TP 3
Types:

Subject = iodata() | \fBunicode:charlist()\fR\&
.br
RE = \fBmp()\fR\& | iodata() | \fBunicode:charlist()\fR\&
.br
Replacement = iodata() | \fBunicode:charlist()\fR\&
